{"tid":1878094,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"［教學］教大家點樣擺脫人類嘅軀殼，成為神","createTime":"2020-02-13T11:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T12:05:39.000Z","uid":42927,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bf8382f0790871d3a84b43dd1767c90a508973b7","tid":1878094,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:41:42.000Z","msg":"簡單嚟講有三個步驟：<br />\n<br />\n1.你係人<br />\n2.做啲人做唔到嘅嘢<br />\n3.成為神<br />\n<br />\n首先 1. 相信依個大部分連登仔都做到, 除咗啲波台會員之外<br />\n<br />\n但之後嘅 2. 依個比較難做到, 咁我解釋下啦 <br />\n<br />\n一般嚟講, 人做到嘅嘢係人都做到, 如果做唔到嘅就係人做唔到嘅嘢, 即係傳說中嘅''超越身體的極限'' <br />\n<br />\n接著落嚟, 我可以教大家試下一個方法去''超越身體的極限'', <br />\n<br />\n注意十六歲以下小朋友切勿模仿!!!<br />\n<br />\n請伸出舌頭, 然後試下用盡力將舌頭掂下巴, 並大啖大啖咁抖氣, <br />\n<br />\n依個時候如果成功你就會feel到自己嘅頭髮開始變金並且飛起, <br />\n<br />\n恭喜你! 你已經可以去到成為神嘅地步, <br />\n<br />\n但如果失敗, 你就係on9仔啦哈哈!!<br />\n<br />\n最後, 去到3. 嘅時候你已經係神, 但請留意! 神都有分幾種, 睇你想成為乜嘢嘅神, <br />\n<br />\n咁你係需要選擇一下, 然後向住個天大叫：我想做X神 <br />\n<br />\n（ X 係你想成為嘅神）<br />\n<br />\n例如你做想做軒達臣, 咁你就要大叫：我想做軒達臣!<br />\n<br />\n咁就得㗎啦~ 如是者你就係一個合資格嘅神<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上就係點樣成為神嘅教學, 希望大家都可以早日成為神啦~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有任何問題唔明, 歡迎大家問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64eef1519b57d08490b87059eb554fa1206ab81","tid":1878094,"uid":136527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:45:18.000Z","msg":"我想做Eason~"},{"pid":"cc452bdc27117827aae09c5925e07d5c87e5ca3f","tid":1878094,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d64eef1519b57d08490b87059eb554fa1206ab81","tid":1878094,"uid":136527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:45:18.000Z","msg":"我想做Eason~"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:48:29.000Z","msg":"good👍"},{"pid":"6a39b6ef9ecf6d7661210f82590230f2113cb43d","tid":1878094,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:53:08.000Z","msg":"認真教學post冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017758375282317436ea297e045c94c3000fc84c","tid":1878094,"uid":173307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:54:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d5ad82ca7e998b25d9b98bbff12a4396fd577a1","tid":1878094,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:54:40.000Z","msg":"你班低賤嘅人類，仲諗住拯救你哋逃離苦海！<br />\n<br />\n點知你哋都係執迷不悟！<br />\n<br />\n成世做低賤嘅人類啦！<br />\n<br />\n早知唔能教你哋。"},{"pid":"1da595f7c8e9e341d996207e55e47db16ba22988","tid":1878094,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"017758375282317436ea297e045c94c3000fc84c","tid":1878094,"uid":173307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:54:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:55:04.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母呀！🖕"},{"pid":"5f8e7dada4260497a33b79437b9aa35be565a9dd","tid":1878094,"uid":19487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:55:39.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"8d10041d4679f88efd743e73057f5d7b625828a6","tid":1878094,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f8e7dada4260497a33b79437b9aa35be565a9dd","tid":1878094,"uid":19487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:55:39.000Z","msg":"On9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:56:34.000Z","msg":"why😣"},{"pid":"7057c57077fc52fd29c8d5ac20c23400cca624a1","tid":1878094,"uid":173307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:57:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e028ffbbc98b16fcf8ba4eb7d38e9ba64d75f3df","tid":1878094,"uid":195601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:58:48.000Z","msg":"Pull"},{"pid":"a75afb1738584fbe1e320e45c825e0869fd2973b","tid":1878094,"uid":19487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d10041d4679f88efd743e73057f5d7b625828a6","tid":1878094,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f8e7dada4260497a33b79437b9aa35be565a9dd","